<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Travel App</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4F46E5;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4F46E5;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-note {
            background-color: #EFF6FF;
            border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Travel App!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{ username }}!</h2>
        
        <p>Your {{ role }} account has been created successfully. You now have access to our travel planning platform.</p>
        
        <div class="security-note">
            <strong>üîê Security Notice:</strong> For your security, no password was set during account creation. Please use the link below to create your secure password.
        </div>
        
        <p>To complete your account setup and choose your password, please click the button below:</p>
        
        <a href="{{ resetLink }}" class="button">Set Your Password</a>
        
        <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px;">{{ resetLink }}</p>
        
        <p><strong>This link will expire in 1 hour</strong> for security reasons. If you don't set your password within this time, please contact an administrator.</p>
        
        {% if role == 'admin' %}
        <div style="background-color: #FEF3C7; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <strong>üëë Administrator Access:</strong> You have been granted administrator privileges. With great power comes great responsibility!
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        
        <p>Once you've set your password, you can log in and start planning your adventures!</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Travel App Team</p>
            <p><small>If you didn't expect this email, please contact our support team immediately.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
